title: Copy/Paste failure under wayland/KDE
body:
When run under wayland with kde/plasma as the compositor, copy/paste using ctrl-shift-{C,V} does not work.
This is a regression from 0.4.3.

### System

OS: Linux (Fedora 32)
Version tested: 92ea355eeea538bd868eaebdc03469630aba281c
Works in: c723247c26d00e26d645cb97fa7c73b65260aef3

Logs are from opening a terminal; selecting a word from the command prompt text; hitting ctrl-shift-C, ctrl-shift-V; then ctrl-c if it worked; then ctrl-D to exit.
